Mereka bertiga bersahabat dan berjanji untuk mengembara bersama dan saling mengenali antara satu sama lain. Sebelum kembali ke pengkalan angkasa di bumi, mereka perlu menghadapi pelbagai cabaran mengenai sains dan teknologi terlebih dahulu. Kebijaksanaan Max terbatas dan memerlukan pertolongan rakan-rakannya dalam menyelesaikan misi tersebut.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep13
programme.desc: Yasmin menggunakan Erina untuk mendapatkan semula Syarikat YAS dari datuknya, namun ditolak datuknya menolak. Tibatiba muncul Amar yang baru kembali dari Amerika tanpa memberitahu terlebih dahulu. Amar telah sembuh sepenuhnya dari sakit saraf. Rusdi memberitahu kepada Yasmin dia telah berkahwin dengan Sherry sebagai isteri kedua. Yasmin tidak dapat menerimanya, berlaku pertengkaran dengan suaminya, Rusdi mahu membalas dendam dengan kelakuan Yasmin yang terlalu pentingkan diri sendiri. Yasmin mengalami tekanan perasaan sehingga membuat dirinya separuh gila. Sofia masih belum mengetahui kisah sebenarnya Amar, Iqbal meminta pemuda tersebut bertemu dengan Sofia dan memaklumkan keadaan sebenar dirinya. Amar mengetahui dari bapanya bahawa dia sudah mempunyai anak hasil perkahwinan dengan Sofia bernama Khalif. Amar ingin kembali dengan Sofia, namun Sofia menolak dan meminta Erina mengahwini Amar semula, dia sanggup menjadi rakan baik mereka. Yasmin pula terpaksa mendapatkan rawatan kerana telah hilang waras akibat tekanan perasaan

programme.title: Pengantinku Jatuh Dari Langit S1 Ep18
programme.desc: Arfy menerima panggilan daripada mamanya yang berada di London untuk pulang bercuti di Malaysia selama dua minggu. Arfy kelihatan sangat teruja dan tak sabar menunggu kedatangan mamanya. Hari itu Arfy ajak Rinieta untuk keluar membeli barang keperluan dapur untuk persiapan. Rinieta teringatkan arwah ibunya bila Arfy banyak bercerita tentang mamanya.

programme.title: Pembancuh Kopi Mr Vampire S1 Ep04
programme.desc: Irsyad membelikan kasut baru (sneakers) untuk Nuzul kerana kasut Nuzul sudah lusuh. Nuzul masih blur dengan apa yang terjadi antara dirinya dan Irsyad. Kawan-kawan Nuzul di Rayyan Caf mula mengusik tentang hubungan Nuzul dan Irsyad dan Nuzul rasa tidak sedap hati. Melati mendapat berita tentang Irsyad yang pergi membeli-belah dengan seorang wanita dari temannya yang terserempak dengan Irsyad. Melati memberitahu ibunya tentang hal ini. Datin Maizah akan memikirkan cara bagaimana mahu mendapatkan Irsyad untuk Melati. Tiga minggu kemudian, sejak dari hari Irsyad meluahkan perasaannya pada Nuzul, Irsyad masih belum menunjukkan mukanya lagi pada Nuzul. Nuzul mula rasa rindu namun dia pendamkan sendiri. Tanpa pengetahuan Nuzul, Irsyad telah meminta bantuan Saiful dan Laila untuk membawa Nuzul ke majlis makan malam Garuda Corporation. Irsyad membeli satu set baju yang sangat cantik untuk Nuzul pakai pada malam tersebut. Laila memberitahu Nuzul bahawa mereka akan ke majlis perkahwinan. Nuzul yang tidak mengsyaki apa-apa hanya menurut saja. Tiba di hotel, Nuzul terkejut melihat dewan yang dihias indah dan suasana dewan tersebut tidak seperti majlis perkahwinan. Apa yang mengejutkan Nuzul lagi adalah kemunculan Puan Sri Ayuni dan Tan Sri Jeffri Lee yang menyambutnya dengan gembira. Dia berjalan menuju ke arah Nuzul dan melamar Nuzul menjadi isterinya. Nuzul kaku.

programme.title: The Trial
programme.desc: Ronald, seorang pelajar cacat mental, dituduh merogol Bessy, tutor dan guru sekolahnya. Dan apabila sekolah memfailkan kes terhadap Ronald dalam usaha untuk melemparkannya ke penjara, keluarga Ronald diberi beberapa pilihan berharga dalam hal pembelaan undang-undang. Tetapi sebagai pelajar darjah tujuh berusia 29 tahun, Ronald adalah "kes khas" dalam lebih daripada satu cara.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep18
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Daniel, Adam dan Shah meneruskan pemburuan lembaga drama. Mereka juga berjumpa dengan pengarah dan set krew yang sedang membuat penggambaran. Daripada pengarah itu, mereka dapat maklum penggambaran mereka sering terganggu kerana kehadiran lembaga. Setelah dapat nasihat rupanya lembaga drama minat berlakon. Berikutan itu, mereka bertiga berpakat dengan pengarah di set penggambaran supaya jangan takut apabila kemunculannya, sebaliknya berpakat dan membawa lembaga itu terus ke muzium hantu Bad. Caranya berhelah kononnya set penggambaran akan dilakukan di situ. Kemudiannya pengarah berjaya membawa lembaga itu di depan muzium. Di situ lembaga drama akhirnya dapat diberkas. Kini penggambaran filem tidak terganggu lagi dan en. Bad terus gembira dengan koleksi baru iaitu lembaga drama. Sebelum itu ibu Nur yang berbaik dengan Azman telah memutuskan hubungan mereka kerana Azman sebenarnya seorang yang sedang mengalami tekanan perasaan. Nur masih tidak puas hati sikap bapanya yang meneruskan suka bersahabat dengan wanita lebih muda. Secara kebetulan Nur telah berjumpa dengan Ustaz Ali dan mula belajar ilmu keagamaan secara percuma di situ.

programme.title: Mumun
programme.desc: Mumun dan Juned adalah pasangan yang saling menyayangi. Walau bagaimanapun, Mumun meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan dan Juned sangat kecewa dengannya.

programme.title: The Closet
programme.desc: Selepas anak perempuan Sang-Won, Yi-Na hilang di rumah baharu mereka, seorang lelaki misteri menghampirinya dan menyuruhnya mencarinya di dalam almari.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Bad pada mulanya bersiar-siar dan Nur, anaknya pula memesan ayam golek. Bad singgah di Kg. Paling Sweet, di gerai Leman dan membeli ayam golek. Dari Leman maklumat tentang lembaga Senyum diperolehi. Encik Bad berminat dengan kisah itu, setelah mendapat maklumat lanjut dia telah mengarahkan ketiga-tiga pekerjanya supaya mendapat maklumat selanjutnya dari Leman. Yang penting misi mereka menangkap lembaga Senyum. Adam, Daniel dan Shah telah ditunjukkan rumah asal lembaga Periang, bapa lembaga Senyum. Selain itu Leman menceritakan serba ringkas latar belakang lembaga Periang dan beberapa mangsa pernah diganggu oleh lembaga senyum. Berikutan itu Adam, Shah dan Daniel telah masuk ke kawasan kampung itu dengan kereta lengkap dengan peralatan serta keupayaan mereka untuk memerangkap lembaga senyum. Sementara itu Nur terus menjadi tali penghubung di antara bapa dan ibunya. Bapanya menerima kiriman ibunya, tetapi menunjukkan tidak berapa suka. Waktu lapang, Shah akan menghubungi dengan kekasihnya melalui khidmat pesanan ringkas. Pun begitu tetap merahsiakan kepada Adam.

programme.title: Marai Mugam
programme.desc: Filem komedi Tamil Malaysia arahan Sara. R fdam (RMS), dibintangi oleh ahli pasukan RMS. Filem ini dirakam di pelbagai lokasi terkenal dan bersejarah seperti Dataran Merdeka, King`s Palace Kuala Lumpur, Pulau Besar Melaka, Taiping Perak, Seremban dan juga beberapa tempat lain di Malaysia. Muzik untuk filem ini digubah oleh Jay Raggaveindra, pengarah muzik Malaysia.

programme.title: Terowong Ep9
programme.desc: Episod 9 ini bertajuk "Cantik" memaparkan adegan Nani menjadi igauan Yusry yang tertidur di pejabat. Jeritan Yusry yang ternampak Nani sebagai hantu memeranjatkan rakan-rakannya yang lain. Nani yang juga mendengar jeritan tersebut memarahi Yusry kerana mengatakan dia sebagai hantu. Sejak dari peristiwa tersebut Yusry mula tergilakan Nani yang kelihatan bertambah cantik. Perkara ini menyebabkan Sidah iri hati. Bagi Nani beliau telah berjaya menjadi cantik dengan menggunakan khidmat bomoh Tok Mok dengan memakaikan beliau susuk. Sidah yang tidak puas hati dengan kecantikan Nani menemui Bomoh Tok Mok. Beliau diberitahu pantang larang bagi orang yang memakai susuk. Nani kena banyak berpantang terutama mesti dengar cakap pendamping yang telah sisyaratkan oleh bomoh Tok Moh. Setelah pantang larang tersebut dilanggar oleh Nani serta dan menyebabkan wajah Nani kembali menjadi hodoh seperti asal.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep12
programme.desc: Episod 12 memaparkan kisah lucu bagaimana Sohot telah dibawa oleh jin bernama Rakib ke suatu tempat hingga kawan-kawanya susah hati dan menyatakan bahawa dia telah disorok oleh bunian. Rakib telah membawa Salim ke suatu tempat yang sama Sohot sampai terlebih dahulu dan kemudian jin Rakib telah meminjam badan Salim untuk mendampingi Hariman. Sohot telah kembali kepangkuan Hariman dan Salim, sementara Cikgu Razif keluar makan bersama Maira, Imran dan Suraya, emak Maira. Hariman telah meminta Salim mencari buloh untuk dibuat layang layang khas untuk Haikal kerana hendak mengambil hatinya sementara Zara dan Haikal sedang mencari buloh untuk membuat layang-layang

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Beberapa dekad selepas sebuah gereja rock di Carpathians Romania yang komunis runtuh apabila ekspedisi menyebabkan tanah runtuh dan menimbus semua orang, pasukan saintifik Dr. Nicolai yang meneroka legenda pertempuran raksasa Templar Knights yang berkaitan menemui sistem gua yang dalam dan banjir dan mengupah adik beradik Jack dan penyelam cemerlang Tyler pasukan untuk menerokainya. Satu lagi letupan memerangkap mereka, selepas menemui parasit misteri yang mengubah semua spesies karnivor, dan kemudian spesies pemangsa yang berkembang secara bebas. Jack mungkin dijangkiti dan beralih, tetapi Tyler tetap dengannya, jadi kumpulan itu berpecah, diburu oleh raksasa, yang juga terbang.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep1
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan pasangan suami dan isteri, Zahid dan Sabrina, masih belum mempunyai anak kerana kehamilan Sabrina telah beberapa kali gugur. Kini, Sabrina mengalami ketekanan dan sering mimpi ngeri serta diganggu oleh bunyi yang ganjil. Zahid berasa bosan dengan Sabrina kerana selalu menceritakan mimpi ngeri. Tanpa diketahui Sabrina, Zahid dan Suria, seorang rakan Sabrina, telah menjalinkan perhubungan sulit.

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Beberapa dekad selepas sebuah gereja rock di Carpathians Romania yang komunis runtuh apabila ekspedisi menyebabkan tanah runtuh dan menimbus semua orang, pasukan saintifik Dr. Nicolai yang meneroka legenda pertempuran raksasa Templar Knights yang berkaitan menemui sistem gua yang dalam dan banjir dan mengupah adik beradik Jack dan penyelam cemerlang Tyler pasukan untuk menerokainya. programme.title: You Saka.. Pergi Jauh Jauh Ep1
programme.desc: Episod Pertama cereka komedi seram disusuli dengan kepercayaan khurafat ini berkisar kepada personaliti Nia. Nia sebagai setiausaha syarikat milik seorang Datin Salina yang amat menyukainya hingga bercadang untuk dijodohkan kepada anak lelakinya. Ibu Nia dikampung, sedang sakit dijagai oleh Roslan, bapa saudaranya (Pak Lang). Nia mempercayai dia wajar menyeru puteri yang sesekali Nia akan lakukan bertujuan melindunginya dan juga sebagai amalan turun temurunnya selama ini. Jika tidak dilakukan, saka berbentuk syaitan akan menggangguinya. Ada sebab-sebab bahawa ibunya memiliki saka dan kematiannya bererti saka itu cuba mempengaruhi warisnya iaitu Nia. Nia tinggal dengan Shasa dan sepupu Shasa iaitu, Adrus adalah 'boy friend' Nia. Adrus sedang menceburi kerjaya dalam bidang paranormal, merupakan anak Ibrahim seorang bomoh. Ketika ibu Nia meninggal dunia dia belum ketahui. Sementara itu, semasa pengembumian ibunya berlaku juga kekecuhan iaitu muncul lembaga putih (berbentuk manusia - wanita). Selain dari itu, sesekali saka Gelam berbentuk syaitan (hitam jalur hijau) mengganggui Nia, 'boy friend'nya dan pernah bersama lembaga putih mengganggui bomoh Ibrahim.

programme.title: London Has Fallen
programme.desc: Di London untuk pengebumian Perdana Menteri, Mike Banning terperangkap dalam plot untuk membunuh semua pemimpin dunia yang hadir.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep1
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Hawa (ibu Halim) yang datang dari kampung, menasihati Hawa dan Nina supaya menerima takdir. Halim merasakan dia boleh mengendalikan pemasalahannya sama Nina itu dengan caranya. Hawa yang menyedari anaknya itu diganggu sesuatu menasihatkani Hawa supaya berubat tetapi tidak diendahkan. Halim merasa bosan dengan ibunya dan menghantar pulang ke kampung

programme.title: Anak Jantan
programme.desc: Anak Jantan menceritakan kisah Darin yang dihantui oleh kehidupan yang lalu. Gaya hidup negatifnya berubah sama sekali apabila beliau jatuh cinta kepada seorang wanita dari kampungnya bernama Nara. Tidak lama kemudian, pasangan ini berhijrah ke bandar KL untuk memulakan kehidupan baru. Mereka dikurniakan seorang anak lelaki yang bijak bernama Saufi. Malangnya, kebahagiaan keluarga mereka tidak bertahan lama dengan ketibaan Somchai, seorang rakan lama yang kembali menyebabkan pergolakan di tempat kerja Darin.

programme.title: Check In Shock
programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang berkumpul di hospital terbiar untuk mengambil bahagian dalam rancangan realiti. Sesiapa yang berjaya bermalam di tempat yang dikatakan berhantu akan memenangi hadiah wang tunai. Apabila malam semakin larut, sesetengah daripada mereka mula mengesyaki bahawa penganjur tidak bercadang untuk membenarkan sesiapa pergi dengan ganjaran. Kebenaran ternyata lebih mengancam apabila roh yang menghantui tempat itu terbukti benar dan mula menyerang mereka.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep14
programme.desc: Memaparkan Shah, Adam dan Daniel terus mengesan lembaga baju yang memakai baju budaya Jepun dan satu malam mereka ternampaknya dan rupanya cantik. Mereka tidak gunakan senjata biasa tetapi menggunakan taktik memujuk. Mereka gagal juga, lembaga itu terus menghilang. Di waktu siang, Shah secara kebetulan bertemu Ana dan Shah seperti biasa cuba merayu dan memikatnya. Kebetulan Adam ternampak lebih-lebih kelihatan Ana menyukai Shah semula. Bila Ana beredar, Adam bersemuka meminta Shah memaklumkan tentang Nur. Adam tidak setuju. Dalam pada itu janda yang berbaik dengan Bad terus akrab, Nur tidak menyukainya lalu menceritakan kepada ibunya. Ibunya hanya menyokong sekurang-kurangnya Nur akan mudah. Encik Tar masih memujuk encik Bad untuk bergabung sebaliknya encik Bad masih memberi alasan sedang berfikir dan dia juga meminta pandangan janda yang suka mendekainya. Oleh kerana sukar lembaga baju di perangkap Shah, Adam dan Daniel memerangkap lembaga Jepun dahulu. Dengan kerjasama lembaga Jepun akhirnya kembaga baju dapat diperangkap mereka. Kini Sabariah dan suaminya senang hati.

programme.title: Anak Jantan
programme.desc: Anak Jantan menceritakan kisah Darin yang dihantui oleh kehidupan yang lalu. Gaya hidup negatifnya berubah sama sekali apabila beliau jatuh cinta kepada seorang wanita dari kampungnya bernama Nara. Tidak lama kemudian, pasangan ini berhijrah ke bandar KL untuk memulakan kehidupan baru. Mereka dikurniakan seorang anak lelaki yang bijak bernama Saufi. Malangnya, kebahagiaan keluarga mereka tidak bertahan lama dengan ketibaan Somchai, seorang rakan lama yang kembali menyebabkan pergolakan di tempat kerja Darin.

programme.title: Marai Mugam
programme.desc: Filem komedi Tamil Malaysia arahan Sara. R fdam (RMS), dibintangi oleh ahli pasukan RMS. Filem ini dirakam di pelbagai lokasi terkenal dan bersejarah seperti Dataran Merdeka, King`s Palace Kuala Lumpur, Pulau Besar Melaka, Taiping Perak, Seremban dan juga beberapa tempat lain di Malaysia. Muzik untuk filem ini digubah oleh Jay Raggaveindra, pengarah muzik Malaysia.

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Beberapa dekad selepas sebuah gereja rock di Carpathians Romania yang komunis runtuh apabila ekspedisi menyebabkan tanah runtuh dan menimbus semua orang, pasukan saintifik Dr. Nicolai yang meneroka legenda pertempuran raksasa Templar Knights yang berkaitan menemui sistem gua yang dalam dan banjir dan mengupah adik beradik Jack dan penyelam cemerlang Tyler pasukan untuk menerokainya. programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep8
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Adam, Shah Daniel meneruskan usaha pengesanan lembaga senyum dengan bantuan Leman. Secara kebetulan mengikut "Whatsapp Group" Leman bahawa lembaga senyum baru ke rumah Mak Jemah. Kumpulan Adam bergegas ke situ. Mereka dapat mengesannya di rumah Mak Jamah beberapa kali tetapi menghilangkan diri. Mereka gagal. Setelah gagal mereka merujuk kepada Prof. Setelah mendapat penerangan dan kaedah, mereka telah menyiapkan beberapa peralatan permainan kanak-kanak demi untuk menangkap lembaga itu. Pun begitu masih gagal. Sementara itu, Nur terus memujuk bapa dan ibunya supaya makan malam dengan alasan mereka telah sekian lama tidak makan bersekali. Adam, Shah dan Daniel yang gagal kali ini mendapat penerangan daripada penjaga "parking", kononnya dia dulunya pawang, Adam dinasihati memakai jubah hitam. Dengan kaedah itu akhirnya Daniel dan Shah berjaya memerangkap lembaga senyum iaitu ketika Adam seolah bertindak sebagai bapanya. Bad terus gembira dan membenarkan mereka bertiga bercuti.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep15
programme.desc: Memaparkan Shah dan Adam bertelagah kerana Shah ingin menonton wayang dengan rakan barunya. Adam marahkan Shah yang bersikap playboy. Shah mulanya menonton wayang dengan Ana kemudiannya berbohong Ana kerana Nur pula datang untuk menonton wayang juga. Setakat ini helah Shah masih dapat menyakinkan Nur dan Ana. Dalam masa yang sama Bad tahu yang Tar diburu "along" jadi pujukannya untuk bergabung gagal. Dia juga muflis. Ini membuatkan Tar berpakat dengan seseorang iaitu bomoh moden dan kini bomoh moden telah menghantar satu lembaga ke dalam muzium Bad. Sementara itu Abang Lut memaklumkan ada lembaga Nengnab. Kemudiannya Adam bersama Shah dan Daniel berbincang dengan Bad lalu Bad setuju mereka memburu lembaga tersebut. Kemudiannya Abang Lut membuat persiapan awal menanti mereka bertiga tiba dan tempat penginapan telah diatur. Sebelum itu Nur yang tidak suka Kiah berkawan dengan bapanya telah berjaya membuat helah kononya bapanya kini sakit otak dan tidak dapat datang ke Muzium. Akibat percaya, Kiah kini menyampaikan pesanan ringkas kepada Bad yang mereka kini tidak perlu berhubung lagi. Dalam misi mengesan lembaga Nengnab, kali pertamanya tidak dapat diteruskan operasinya kerana Shah terlupa "charge battery" pada alat pengesan. Adam yang merajuk balik dahulu ke kenderaan mereka, kesempatan ketika Shah dan Daniel masih berbincang, Adam telah berhubung Nur. Shah tidak tahu kemudiannya mereka bertiga balik ke hotel, Adam diganggu lembaga di bilik tidurnya kebetulan Daniel datang menumpang biliknya selepas itu akibat Shah berdengkur kuat.

programme.title: Ruqyah
programme.desc: Pada pertengahan tahun 2012, Mahisa ingin membantu seorang pelakon bernama Asha yang merasa diganggu oleh roh. Merasakan terlalu banyak kejadian aneh yang dilihatnya, dia yakin Asha sedang dirasuk makhluk ghaib. Selepas berunding dengan seorang ustadz yang terkenal, dia cuba melakukan ruqyah untuk menyucikan Asha. Namun ternyata apa yang dimiliki Asha tidak mudah untuk dilepaskan walaupun menyerang Mahisa. Apa yang dimiliki Asha bertujuan untuk menjadi "menarik" untuk disukai ramai orang. Mahisa juga tertarik dengan Asha.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan kali ini Adam, Shah dan Daniel meneruskan misi untuk mengesan lembaga kuali. Sebelum itu dalam diam-diam Shah bertemu janji dengan Nur dan keluar bersiar-siar di bandar. Mereka telah ke rumah sasaran di rumah Mak Jah. Setakat ini dari pengesanan awal tiada lembaga kuali. Dalam pada itu Bad bertanyakan ibu Nur kepada Nur. Setelah tiada sebarang tanda-tanda di kawasan perumahan Mak Jah, lalu mereka tamatkan pemburuan. Akibat ada gangguan baru di kawasan itu mereka meneruskan pengesanan. Kononnya di gerai makan perumahan itu laris akibat saka yang memasak. Kini lembaga kuali gagal memasuki gerai itu lagi sebaliknya berkeliaran di rumah tertentu. programme.desc: Mengisahkan Rahul telah mati ditembak semasa kumpulan bodyguard di bawah Nasha membuat operasi di sebuah banglo. Operasi ini adalah untuk mendapatkan maklumat kegiatan peminjam wang di lokasi tersebut. Dalam kes yang lain, Farish sebagai bodyguard kepada pelakon Kasandara mendapat layanan baik dari pelakon tersebut. Ini adalah kerana Kasandara mulai terpikat dengan Farish. Danial sebagai bodyguard kepada Yasmin diminta pergi ke rumah Dato Bakar untuk menyiasat kehilangan Yasmin. Datin Rosnah memberitahu anaknya Hakim mempunyai masalah jiwa, dia bimbang Hakim menculik Yasmin kerana hubungannya dengan Yasmin selalu dihalang. Sementara itu, Ryan terus menjaga Haris dari gangguan Samad seorang pemberi pinjaman wang.

programme.title: Azem 3
programme.desc: Seorang isteri cemburu "zehra" meragui suaminya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan rakannya, dia merancang untuk melaksanakan sihir hitam oleh beberapa syeikh yang jahat untuk mendapatkan suaminya kembali daripada pesaingnya. Beberapa siri peristiwa hebat mula berlaku kepada rakannya berakhir dengan pembunuhan "zehra" y suaminya untuk mengelakkan skandal curang.

programme.title: Bopeng
programme.desc: Apabila dua kawan baik, Bo dan Peng mendapat panggilan daripada seorang gadis bernama Mira Idora Senrose dan memberitahu mereka dia telah diculik dan menyaksikan pembunuhan ngeri oleh penculiknya, mereka bekerjasama dalam misi menyelamat dengan bantuan polis.

programme.title: Si Luncai
programme.desc: Cinta ditolak kerana pangkat dan darjat, Si Luncai, sang pengembala kambing pergi dengan harapan yang hancur. Dirinya yang lurus dipermainkan oleh Ketua Kampung - namun kejadian tersebut telah membawanya ke seorang nenek kebayan yang telah mengubah hidupnya. Si Luncai menyamar menjadi tukang tabib dan mempermainkan semula Ketua Kampung itu. Berjayakah rancangan Si Luncai untuk mendapatkan cintanya?

programme.title: Operasi Cegah Jenayah
programme.desc: Dua orang anggota polis, Shah dan Din telah ditugaskan untuk mengawasi satu pertunjukan permata berlian yang bernilai jutaan ringgit. Pihak penganjur juga meminta mereka berdua menjaga para peragawati mereka yang sedang bercuti daripada pertunjukan itu. Dalam masa yang sama, Crystal yang menjadi pengurus agensi peragawati itu merancang satu rompakan barangan berharga yang berada dalam pengawasan Shah dan Din.

programme.title: Cikgu Sayang
programme.desc: Seorang guru muda bernama Idayu telah dihantar ke sebuah kampung di Pulau Dinawan untuk mengajar sekolah orang dewasa. Di sana, Idayu telah digelarkan sebagai Cikgu Sayang oleh pelajarnya. Kehadiran Idayu di pulau itu telah menimbulkan perasaan cemburu kepada isteri para pelajarnya. Dalam masa yang sama, Idayu mula tertarik dengan seorang pemuda bernama Anuar yang tinggal di pulau itu.

programme.title: Rimba Malam
programme.desc: Sofea, seorang gadis jutawan diburu oleh orang-orang Farouk untuk membunuhnya. Satu kemalangan yang disengajakan telah membuatkan Sofea terdampar di tengah-tengah hutan belantara di Kalimantan. Farouk dan orang-orangnya masih memburu Sofea apabila mengetahui dia masih hidup dan tinggal di sebuah perkampungan orang hulu di sana. Sofea sempat menyelamatkan diri atas pertolongan Rafi, pemuda kampung itu ketika Farouk datang mencarinya.

programme.title: Serampang Tiga
programme.desc: Pak Guntor menghantar anaknya, Indra untuk pergi mendamaikan sebuah kampung dan bertemu adiknya, Naneng. Indra ditemani rakannya, Jalur dalam perjalanan itu. Setibanya mereka di kampung itu, mereka membantu Kiambang dan ayahnya yang diganggu sekumpulan orang jahat. Indra menemui adiknya namun dia telah mati dibunuh. Indra berjanji untuk menuntut bela kematian adiknya.

programme.title: Sayang Salmah
programme.desc: Semangat cinta akan bangsa dan negara diterapkan dalam diri Hassan dan Salleh selaku anak kepada Encik Jabar dan Dasimah yang inginkan anak mereka mempunyai rasa patriotik akan negara. Hassan, aktif dalam bidang politik manakala Salleh menjadi seorang pemuda liar yang suka berhibur. Segalanya berubah apabila ayah mereka meninggal dunia.

Sarah ingin membuka semula kes bapanya dan membawa Zaid ke muka pengadilan dengan mendapatkan bantuan seorang bekas banduan.

programme.desc: Diutuskan oleh Baginda Sultan untuk mengamankan sebuah desa yang sedang bergolak angkara pendekar yang jahat, Pendekar Helang sengaja mencetuskan huru-hara supaya tidak disyaki oleh Pendekar Daing yang kejam. Pendekar Daing sering mencuri harta orang kampung dan juga menculik anak dara sebagai tahanannya lalu mencetuskan kacau bilau kepada orang di desa itu. Sengaja melakukan perjanjian bersamanya, Pendekar Helang mengambil Sundang Panca Sakti yang dikatakan mampu membunuh pendekar jahat itu dari simpanan Penghulu Malim untuk diberi kepada Pendekar Daing sebagai muslihat untuk membunuhnya. programme.desc: Be a "shark", if you're a woman, to survive in your working and personal relationship? DU,AI-SHA, also known as Shark, is aggressive and ruthless YI,FEI-YANG nickname is "Orca". Orcas kills sharks. That implies the relationship between them. They are friends and foes at the same time. They show no mercy and never surrender. Love comes and goes but friendship lasts forever. AI-SHA doesn't want to lose her best friend YI,FEI-YANG. She doesn't need love, but she needs him.

programme.title: Player in Kaohsiung (M) Ep4647
programme.desc:
The name Kaohsiung has entered into a century of history since it has been renamed from Da Gou. This year, the National Day fireworks will be held again in Kaohsiung after 20 years passed. SETI has specially produced a new travelogue for Kaohsiung, leading the audience to visit the most popular, charming, and unique places in Kaohsiung. Through the lens, the century-old glory of Kaohsiungs [One-Hundred] is presented profoundly.
The new season of "Player in Kaohsiung" invites many hosts and celebrities, including Yao Yao, Chang Chin Lan, Daniel Chen, David Wu, Ada Chang, Fay Wu, and Kua Kua, visit the 38 administrative districts of Kaohsiung to explore the sensational stories of the people in the alleys, deeply explore the professional spirit of the Greater Kaohsiung area, the traditions and customs of the aboriginal people, the living beside the farms and ports, and the humanism nurtured by Kaohsiungs century-old history.

programme.title: iWalker-Moving Kitchen (M)(repeat) Ep14
programme.desc: Tuesday "iWalker" has been upgraded and changed the name into "iWalker-Moving Kitchen". James and the pretty chef, Rachel will move to different province with the mobile kitchen which costs more than 2 million NTD, and introduce to the audience the unique taste of the province.

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: Undercover Hidden Dragon
programme.desc: In this hilarious comedy, Fat is a gangster who suffers from amnesia. Believing that he is actually an undercover policeman, Fat attempts to arrest gang leader Big Bro, but instead becomes the gangsters best ally. To complicate matters further, a gangster named Wind, who looks exactly like Fat, starts a turf war with Big Bro.

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: The Knight of Shadows: Between Yin and Yang
programme.desc: Pu Song Ling, a legendary demon hunter, is asked to investigate a case involving missing teenage village girls with disciple, Constable Yan Fei. The duo leads a group of little monsters to help with the investigation, and in their search for the truth, they accidentally discover a mysterious love between a knight and a female ghost.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: The Rise of Hero
programme.desc: Young Wong Fei Hung studies hard for an exam in Guangzhou to win a chance to study abroad. However, Eunuch Hai plans to abort the overseas project and this conflict evolves into a real fight. Wong finally defeats Hai on his own and ensure the smooth continuation of the Study Abroad Campaign.

programme.title: Needing You
programme.desc: Office politics and love between co-workers complicates the lives of two computer-company employees in this romantic comedy starring Andy Lau and Sammi Cheng.

programme.title: Horseplay
programme.desc: Ha Mui goes to London to track down an art thief, Nine-Tailed Fox, who is interested in a pottery horse from the Tang Dynasty. Cheung Ho is a cop who chases after Nine-Tailed Fox since he escaped years ago. The trio must work together to gain the pottery, with Nine-Tailed Fox being hunted by his rivals at the same time.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Miao Miao
programme.desc: Miao Miao is an awkward young beauty who nevertheless enchants her outgoing classmate Xiao Ai. As Xiao Ais feelings for Miao Miao grows from friendship to something more, Miao Miao discovers her own burgeoning attraction to a sullen CD store owner, and quietly pursues him.

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are gambling addicts who have come across each other a few times at the casino, but do not leave impression on each other until they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau. They find themselves falling in love, and decide to get married when they come back to Hong Kong.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kits master, Debo.

programme.title: American Dreams in China
programme.desc: During the economic reform period in the 80s, three undergraduates are brought together by a common ambition to live the American dream.

programme.title: When Sun Meets Moon
programme.desc: In 1992, a heavy rainstorm caused a massive power outage in Hong Kong. Two young astrology enthusiasts, Moon and Sun, met on that starry night and fell in love. However, the path to love is not an easy one and they would need to endure parental objections and overcome challenges from teachers and friends.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: Love · Revolution
programme.desc: Ai Yoshida will do anything for love, including traveling to Thailand with her boyfriend from Japan to run dope. When her boyfriend is kidnapped by the local gangster after a brawl at a bar, Ai sets out on a rescue mission that sends her on an action-packed roller-coaster ride where she meets a professional assassin who breaks out of jail for love.

programme.title: Fall in Love at First Kiss
programme.desc: In this romantic love story starring Taiwanese actors Darren Wang and Jelly Lin, an ordinary girl develops a stubborn crush on the school genius after an unexpected kiss. But with the genius adored by everyone in the school, can their relationship blossom and develop?

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the midnight gymnasium programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it. With an ex-star athlete John as the coach, the girls realize they must face their problems and overcome their challenges instead of dodging them. Can they finally win the match?

programme.title: Princess & 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: The New Big Boss
programme.desc: A young man seeks out the Wolf, a legendary undefeated warrior. When he sees that the Wolf is now an old man, he prompts him to retell his past glories.

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: Golden Chicken
programme.desc: Ah Kam, a seasoned prostitute, gets locked inside an ATM vestibule with a thief. Both discover they are ill-fated in life and Ah Kam starts telling him her life story as a prostitute, from a teenage hooker to a PR girl in an upscale club in her thirties, as well as being a strip dancer, bar girl and masseuse.

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Aberdeen
programme.desc: The Cheng family embodies a microcosm of Hong Kong, with its contradictions between tradition and modernity, superstition and materialism, family and individual. The movie reveals troubled characters dealing with their own issues in the city, from the eldest, Taoist priest patriarch Dong; to the youngest, the bullied elementary schooler Chloe.

programme.title: Rise of the Legend
programme.desc: The young Wong Fei Hung is a fearless fighter who aligns himself with one of the two gang leaders ruling Guangzhou. However, there is more to the young Wong Fei Hung than meets the eye as he has a more dangerous agenda in mind.

programme.title: The Killer
programme.desc: Hsieh Choun, the Black Dragon, is in trouble with the police since Wang Sien Tien's gang is helping them; he is no longer free to conduct his drugs shipments out of the port freely as he used to. He buys more thugs and killers to dispose of the young upstart, and soon Wang is in dire straits, in the port of Hong Kong.

programme.title: Lover'S Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Lady With A Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman Feng tries to find a group of villains responsible for her eldest sister's death, but is shocked to discover that her fianc, Jin, is one of them. At the same time, Jin's mother and the two other killers are planning to kill Feng. Can Feng fight back and take her revenge?

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Gambler'S Delight
programme.desc: The Killer star Danny Lee plays the lead role of a guy who needs to become a hero. He lies, steals and cheats his way into operating a plush casino, but when he incurs the wrath of a female Japanese gang leader, all bets are off!

programme.title: Double Bliss
programme.desc: Double Bliss tells the story of two students who fall in love and want to wed, but there is one small snag: their parents don't agree! The two ingenious lovebirds come up with what they think is a foolproof plan...They play dead!

programme.title: The King Boxer
programme.desc: This tale of a honorable fighter's retraining in the "Iron Palm" style, that became the first international martial arts movie hit and made a continent-spanning star of Lo Lieh.

programme.title: Asia-Pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: A Friend From Inner Space
programme.desc: A young boy whose parents are separated tries to find happiness in life. One day, he meets and befriends a kind-hearted spirit Ren, who decides to make him truly happy by getting his parents back together.

programme.title: The Black Falcon
programme.desc: Jenny Hu and veteran co-star Margaret Tu Chuan join longtime0020idol Paul Chang Chung in a battle against the notorious Black Falcon crime mob in Singapore. Together they have to face forgery, fire, and even poisoned needles to stop the mob.

programme.title: Two Con Men
programme.desc: Two Con Men is a wonderfully twisted, pseudo-romantic comedy in the vein of "Robin Hood" meets "The Sting". Starring Liang Tien as Clever Chan and Chang Ying (who's done over 400 films) as Tricky Ching, it's the age-old competition between a rookie con artist versus the ultimate, experienced flimflam man. It's a game Chen cannot afford to lose, because people's lives - including his own, hang in the balance of good versus evil.

programme.title: Angel With The Iron Fists
programme.desc: Lo Wei directs and stars as the chief detective in this gripping thriller; playing alongside Lily Ho, who excels in the role of an undercover avenger that can fight as well as she flirts! Caught between the crime bosses known as Baldhead and Black Widow, she only has four choices: punch, kick, shoot or bombard with explosives!

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: Crazy Nuts Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: A roadside bandit and a traveling gambler team up to make money from gambling. In a successful attempt to steal a huge amount of money from a warlords home, they encounter revolutionists who seek their help to fund the reform campaign. Will the two help the revolutionists cause with the stolen money?

programme.title: My Son
programme.desc: Kuo, a polices son, blames his father for his mothers death. He has no job, spends time in night clubs and always gets into fights. One night, Kuo rescues Mei from being raped and they become friends. Kuo wants to support Mei and her family so he goes gambling hoping to gain more money but bad luck seems to be following them with tragic outcomes.

programme.title: Mercenaries From Hong Kong
programme.desc: Filmmaker Wong Jing produced Mercenaries From Hong Kong, his very first modern-day adventure drama. In the dramatic plot he wrote, he sends superstars Ti Lung, Chen Hui-min, Wang Lung-wei, Lo Lieh and Wang Yu on a deadly mission. The film's action sequences are all closely guided by three great kung fu choreographers, led by Tang Chia!

programme.title: Dead End
programme.desc: Uninhibited youth Chun meets a rich girl Wen when her car breaks down and drives her home. Chun falls in love with Wen but Wens brother dislikes him and forbids his sister to see him. He humiliates Chun and gets Chun beaten up, so Chun takes the pistol he has found accidentally on the street to Wens home and shoots her brother dead.

programme.title: To Kill A Jaguar
programme.desc: Set in 1920s Shanghai, a village girl journeys to the big city in search of her father and meets her childhood friend Jaguar, who works for the mob boss Kam. In a world controlled by the mobs, it is a test of survival for all as Jaguar allies himself with ace gunman Ko Tang, to take over Kams empire.

programme.title: Love With The Perfect Stranger
programme.desc: After breaking up with his girlfriend, salesman Bao meets a rich girl, Jin Jin, who just broke up with her boyfriend. Two equally heartbroken strangers fall in love instantly and get married on impulse. The couple lives happily together until Jin Jin finds herself pregnant with her ex-boyfriends baby...

programme.title: Ambush
programme.desc: Constable Wen Chao Fan and his father are framed for a jewel robbery they did not commit. On the run from the law and becoming a wanted fugitive, Wen must recover the jewels in order to clear his family name, but unfortunately he is not the only one seeking the stolen jewels...

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: The Champion
programme.desc: After years in prison, Lu Hu returns home to find himself set up by his ruthless brother Piao, who has taken over the family coal mine business and imprisoned their sister. Hu takes down Piao and saves his sister but their coal mine falls into the hands of a Japanese gang, which Hu and his sister must fight in order to get it back.

programme.title: Sweet And Wild
programme.desc: Fang is a spunky young village girl who is not afraid to fight back against hooligans. She gets into trouble with the biggest hoodlum Tong when she foils his plans with a maid, causing Tong to plot a revenge. Luckily a man whom she is attracted to, Hai, comes in time to her rescue. Can they fight back?

programme.title: The Pearl Phoenix
programme.desc: In Huangmei Opera tradition, this movie tells the love story of Wen, who sells himself as a slave to a rich family, and Huo, the familys young daughter. The lovers are kept apart by Huos stepmother and Huo escapes by dressing up as a man. Wen is framed and put into jail so Huo has to go back and rescue her lover!

programme.title: Inside The Forbidden City
programme.desc: Justice Bao discovers that Consort Lis new born son was swapped at birth and that she was expelled from the palace by Empress Liu twenty years ago. He sets Eunuch Guo up to confess his conspiracy with the Empress. Empress Liu is convicted for her act and Consort Li finally reunites with her son who is now the Emperor.

programme.title: The Fantastic Magic Baby
programme.desc: The story is about the legendary Monkey King (Liu Chung-chun) teams up with Goddess of Mercy (Chao Li-chuan) and the Dragon Girl (Lung Nu) to battle the child god Hung Hai-erh (Ting Hua-chung),son of the Ox Demon (Hung Hai-erh) to rescue Tang Tseng, the Holy Pilgrim (Teng Chio-jen).

programme.title: West Chamber
programme.desc: The story is based on a famous Chinese opera. A young impoverished scholar, Zhang, is enchanted by Hong, the daughter of an influential family whom he meets in a temple. The young couple faces the threat of separation due to her familys objection, so Hongs maid secretly helps to arrange their rendezvous in the West Chamber!

programme.title: Invincible Shaolin
programme.desc: An evil Qing general comes up with a plan to rid the Shaolin masters once and for all. He invites three Northern Shaolin experts to fight against three Southern Shaolin disciples. After the contest, the general secretly kills the Southerners and places the blame on the Northerners. This leads to in-fighting between both Shaolin schools.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: General Feng occupies the city of Shandong, and soldiers and civilians alike welcome him without knowing his tyrannical and lustful nature. His first official business is to inspect the brothels and take the prostitutes home to become his concubines. Feng is finally killed by his officers, but will the new general rule the city differently?

programme.title: My Young Auntie
programme.desc: An elderly landowner marries young Dai Nan to keep his inheritance away from his unscrupulous nephew before he dies. When Dai Nan brings along the deed to meet his other nephew, a series of amusing incidents happen with this young auntie, the nephew and his son. Kara Hui won Best Actress in the first Hong Kong Film Awards for her role as Dai Nan.

programme.title: Diau Charn
programme.desc: In the Han Dynasty, the tyrannical Prime Minister Dong Zuo takes control of the country, so Minister Wang plots to take him down using Diau Charns beauty. Wang arranges for her to be Dongs concubine as he knows Dongs adopted son Lu Bu is in love with her, turning them against each other. Lu Bu ends up killing Dong Zuo to be with Diau Charn.

programme.title: Shaolin Abbot
programme.desc: Monk Chi San is sent by his Shaolin Master to learn a special kung fu from a Wu Dang priest. He gets embroiled in the fight between the Qing and Ming camps and has to gather disciples to rebuild the burnt Shaolin temple at the same time.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: Crippled Avengers
programme.desc: Chu Twin becomes crazy after his sons arms were chopped off. For no reason, he harms four people causing them various disabilities. The four disabled form a band to learn Kung Fu from a master, in order to take revenge on Chu Twin.

programme.desc: Mud Sculptures - It has been raining and the garden is muddy. The tots decide to make mud sculptures. But what will they all do with the sculptures when they are finished?

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep33
programme.desc: How Can I Go Up And Down On The See-Saw? - Baa and Billie have built a fantastic new see-saw in the meadow. Jess can't wait to have a go. But when he tries to make it go up and down with him on one end and Baa and Billie on the other he just gets stuck in the air and can't get the see saw down. How can I go up and down on the see saw?' he asks? -desperate to have all the up and down' fun he see the puppies having when they jump on the see-saw. Jess asks Horace the hoppy frog what he knows about up and down', he talks to Willow about scales and weighing things until finally he works it out if he finds someone roughly the same weight as him balanced just like the puppies were - he'll do it! He works out that Mimi - of all his friends- weighs about the same as him and just as he worked out they jump on the see saw and go up and down, up and down and have a fantastic time! Yippety Yay!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep34
programme.desc: What Can I Do With My Nature Collection? - Jess shows Mimi his lovely Nature Collection. She really likes it and wonders what he's going to do with it. Now that's a good question! Jess thinks he'll display it but with the pups racing around it'd soon get damaged. He asks Horace if he could use it to make musical instruments, some things make a great sound but others aren't so good. It's time to go on a picnic with Mimi and his friends. Jess brings his Nature Collection along and when all his friends want to play a game Jess has a great idea. He's found the perfect thing to do with his Nature Collection! They can use them to make a funny obstacle course race. Brilliant!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep35
programme.desc: How Can I Make My Peach Soft? - JESS and the pups give Baa a peach to eat, thinking it will make a change from grass. But the peach is too hard. How can I make my peach soft? Asks Jess. That's the Big Question! He asks Mimi and watches her kneading clay. She explains she's making the clay soft. Jess tries throwing the peach in the air to soften it but all it does is bruise. Horace tells them that the water in his pond keeps his skin soft so Jess and the pups try to soften the peach in water. But it's still hard. They visit Willow who offers the pups some of her lovely ripe cherries. She explains that the cherries went soft and changed colour when they ripened. Jess realises it's the same for the peach. He waits for it to ripen and then gives it to Baa. It's delicious! And now Jess knows how to make a peach soft. Yippety yay!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep36
programme.desc: How Can We Help Billy Stay Warm? - Jess, Mimi, Baa and Billie are playing a game, kicking a fir cone into a bucket. But it's so cold that poor shivering Billie can't kick properly. They need to find a way Bilie can stay warm enough. Baa's never cold because of his wool. They find a clump of Baa's wool on the ground but it just falls off Billie when Jess puts it on her and Mimi tells them that glueing it on's a bad idea. What happens when it's summer and Billie wants to be cool? Maybe wrapping her in it, like a blanket, is the answer? It definitely keeps her warm - only problem is, she can't move! They realise that Baa wears a scarf as well. Perhaps they need a scarf for Billie? Mimi knits a tiny scarf for Billie, after twisting the clump of wool into yarn. It's perfect! Billie's toasty warm for their game of Flying Fircones. Yippety Yay!

programme.title: Olivia Ep39
programme.desc: Olivia Paints A Mural - Olivia is inspired after a visit to the museum with her family, and decides she's going to become a great painter herself. She gets right down to business, painting a portrait of Ian. When she sees a mural painting on a building wall, she wonders if she'll ever find a space big enough for her big ideas!

programme.title: Olivia Ep40
programme.desc: Olivia And Her Ducklings - After a fun day at the park, Olivia and Ian return home with some unexpected visitors a mother duck and her ducklings! The harder Olivia and Ian try to keep he ducks a secret from Mother and Father, the more household mischief they all seem to get into.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep33
programme.desc: Why Ants Work Together - You see there was a time when Ants didn't work together. The Ants desperately wanted to build themselves a home, but all the animals kept sitting on them, or sneezing them far away or swooping them up into tall trees! On the point of giving up, one brave, young soldier ant rallies the troops Pamoja! Together! Together they can do anything!!! and he was right. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep34
programme.desc: Why Flea Jumps - You see there was a time when Flea didn't jump. Flea didn't really move at all. She was very big and very round. All Flea wanted to do was to see the world. The Tinga Tinga animals try to help lift Flea high up, but she is too heavy. Then Tortoise comes up with an idea Movement and activity!' and after many attempts Flea discovers that she can jump. She can jump really high! Then Flea can jump everywhere and see everything.! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep35
programme.desc: Why Hummingbird Hums - You see there was a time when Hummingbird didn't hum. She was called Songbird and Songbird thought she could sing like a Bird but sadly that was not the case. All the animals tried to help Songbird improve her singing but nothing worked. What could they do?! Then Tortoise has an idea, maybe Songbird can sing without opening her beak!! Songbird agrees and hums the most beautiful hum Tinga Tinga has ever heard. From that day on Songbird was called Hummingbird. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep36
programme.desc: Why Baboon Has A Bare Bottom - You see there was a time when Baboon didn't have a bare bottom and he was very naughty. Baboon loved to play tricks. He played tricks on Elephant. He played tricks on Ostrich. He even dared to play tricks on Lion, the King of Tinga Tinga! And then all the animals decided it was time for the tricks to stop and Baboon to get a dose of his own medicine. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep37
programme.desc: How Can We Hide To Watch Butterflies? - JESS, JOEY and JINX go to the Whispering Woods in the hope of seeing some butterflies, but the puppies are so lively and noisy that they frighten them away. JESS wonders how can we hide to watch butterflies? That's the Big Question! JESS decides to make somewhere to hide out of natural materials. The puppies and Jess try to build a hide out of stones but they're too heavy and all fall down. Jess thinks that something lighter might work well but when they try to build a hide out of straw it's TOO light and flies away in the wind. JESS is stuck - there must be some other material on Greendale Farm they could use. But all that's around them are trees. Jess works out that trees are made out of wood and there are lots of old wooden apple crates in Willow's Stable which will do the job perfectly. JESS, JOEY and JINX build a butterfly hide out of wooden apple crates and soon see lots and lots of beautiful butterflies. Yippety yay!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep38
programme.desc: How Can I Go Faster Than Joey And Jinx? - It's a snowy day on Greendale Farm so Jess and his friends have a race down Cherry Hill. Jess wants to win the race but he can't run as fast in the snow. How can I go faster than Joey and Jinx? Thinks Jess. That's the Big Question. First, Jess tries rolling down the hill like the puppies but he's not a good roller so that doesn't work. Horace shows Jess how he slides down his slide in the pond. Jess tries again at Cherry Hill but can't get going. Helped by Billie and Baa he remembers everything that Horace did - pushing off, going Wheeeee! and lifting his legs up - but nothing works; he ends up sitting in the snow and not sliding at all. He needs something that will move on its own like Mimi's trolley! Jess tries sliding down the hill on the trolley but the wheels get stuck in the snow. Jess decides to take the wheels off and see if the trolley moves faster. Jess whizzes down the hill on the trolley top much faster than the rolling puppies. It's brilliant fun and he's answered the question. Yippety Ya
